{
 "name": "RPlog_Opening_Ceremony",
 "title": "Opening Ceremony",
 "summary": "In the heavily secured Chianar Plaza of New Alderaan on Ord Mantell, a grand opening ceremony and festival draws dignitaries and the public alike beneath a misty sky. Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard takes the podium to address the gathering, a holoprojector displaying the signing of accords between Presav Elana Tracer of the Caspian Union, the Bothan Chief of State Peshk Vry'lya, and the New Republic ambassador. Among the attendees are the strikingly dressed, Imperial-leaning businesswoman Portia Vykos, the sullen young Gabi watched over by a bodyguard, and the smuggler Jaspar, as speeches, performances, food, and dance fill the festive plaza. The event marks a hopeful moment of diplomacy and celebration for the city.",
